!! Citation Watch

This feature tracks publications and authors of interest.

* '''Enable Citation Watch''': Turn the feature on or off.
* '''Tag Name''': The tag you apply to key papers or colleagues to include them in tracking.
* '''Scope''': Choose whether to watch papers, people, or both.

Mark relevant tiddlers with the configured tag to have them monitored automatically.


<div class="tc-config-option">
<$checkbox
  tiddler="$:/config/tw-pubconnector/citationwatch/enable"
  field="text"
  checked="enable"
  unchecked="disable"
  default="disable">
  <$link to="$:/config/tw-pubconnector/citationwatch/enable">
    Enable Citation Watch
  </$link>
</$checkbox>
</div>

  <$link to="$:/config/tw-pubconnector/citationwatch/tag">
    Tag for Citation Watch
  </$link>


<$edit-text
  tiddler="$:/config/tw-pubconnector/citationwatch/tag"
  field="text"
   tag="input" 
  default="Citation Watch"
  placeholder="Citation Watch" />


  <$link to="$:/config/tw-pubconnector/citationwatch/scope">
    Scope for Citation Watch
  </$link>

<$select tiddler="$:/config/tw-pubconnector/citationwatch/scope" default="both">
